  "texts": [
    "The Chatbot interface naturally fits all parts of the story together, making it look complex and logical, which is important in the detective genre.",
    "Sometimes, the plot can be outlined generally, as well as the portraits and roles of the characters.",
    "In this case, the writer should use the AI's answers as drafts or ask clarifying questions, for example: \"Give me more details about this character\", \"What personal drama could he relive?",
    "\", \"What will happen if he chooses to act in that way\".",
    "This approach allows the extraction of new details and makes the plot more intricate and dynamic."
  ],
